Shaun Worthington's car was filmed on a truck's dashcam veering into path of oncoming traffic .
His Audi A4 collided with a truck on the A614 between Burton Agnes and Haisthorpe, near Bridlington, East Yorkshire, on November 19 last year .
The 29-year-old had completed a 12-hour night shift at Cranswick Pet Products in Driffield .
He had recently bought a new phone which did not fit into his previous mobile phone holder .